<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="rothMay1927"><font color="red">Spring 1927</font> <i>Beach Letters</i> (to Sylvia Beach): I signed or endorsed [the cheque] in payment for contributions &lsquo;now appearing&rsquo; but evidently not &lsquo;appearing and to appear&rsquo; for Roth himself in his letter offered to buy other extracts. </div>
